title: Holiday Control & Firing Your Doctor
description:
Jillian lets you know how NOT to blow it! Then Jillian is joined by "The Trusted Voice in Healthcare" Myrtle Potter with some great advice on knowing if it's time to get rid of your doctor and find another.  And as always...it's call time.
